	<!-- About Section -->
    <section id="about" class="bg-light-gray">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-lg-12 text-center">
                    <h2 class="section-heading">About</h2>
                    <h3 class="section-subheading text-muted">Céad Míle Fáilte.</h3>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="row">
            	
            	<div class="col-sm-4 text-justify">
                    <div class="team-member">
                        <img src="assets/team/Live DJ.jpg" class="img-responsive img-circle" alt="">
                        <h4>What We're About'</h4>    
                    </div>
	                    How often do we find ourselves overnight in a different town in this beautiful country of ours and have difficulty finding live
	                    music or indeed a type of music that appeals to us??Likewise, is there anything worse than having a night off or away, spend it 
	                    in a hotel or a bar that has nothing but a juke-box and find out at breakfast the next morning that the pub down the road had an 
	                    excellent band and we missed it!!!! More often than not we've all been in that boat and we have said “Isn’t it a pity their isn’t 
	                    a website out there to list all this?”And now there is…..
                	</div>
                	
                <div class="col-sm-4 text-justify">
                    <div class="team-member">
                        <img src="assets/team/Outdoor Event.jpg" class="img-responsive img-circle" alt="">
                        <h4>Search For Free</h4>
                    </div>
                    	Here at Kilkenny Live we are all about presenting up to date event information to you free of charge.
	                    Simply use out 'Event Finder' to select your preferences, performer, event type, date, time, pick as few or as
	                    many as you like and we'll return events that fit your taste and schedule. If you are on holidays, a weekend away, 
	                    a hen or stag do, not only can you search for events that fit your needs but we also offer directions on our results page
	                    through Google Maps so you don't have to search through your phone or device and start searching locations and 
	                    directions. 
                </div>
                	
                <div class="col-sm-4 text-justify">
                    <div class="team-member">
                        <img src="assets/team/Live Event.jpg" class="img-responsive img-circle" alt="">
                        <h4>We Promote For You</h4> 
                    </div>
                        Here at the Kilkenny Live we offer to promote for venues and performers alike.
                        If you are a venue owner or manager and are looking to expand your business and customer base for events then we're here to help.
                        We can sit down and a discuss your needs and events and then get promoting them for you. We take your information and present it 
                        in a way that accessible to businesses, local people and the tourism sector to make sure that people passionate about live events 
                        know what you have on and when. Feel free to get in contact if you require more information.
                        
                 </div>        
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    
<!-- About Section -->

    <section id="eventfinder">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-xs-12 text-center">
                    <h2 class="section-heading">Event Finder</h2>
                    <h3 class="section-subheading text-muted">Céad Míle Fáilte.</h3>
                 </div>
             </div>
               		<div class="row">
             			<div class="col-md-4 text-center col-md-offset-4">
             				<div class="search-container">
               				
                				<%= form_for @search, html: {class: "pure-form"} do |s|%>
                
			    					<div class="field">
								    	<%= s.label :genre, 'Choose Music/Event Type'%><br>
								    	<%= s.select :genre, options_for_select(@genres), {:prompt => ''}, {:style => 'width: 70%'}%>
								    </div><br>
								    
			    				 <div class="field">
								    	<%= s.label :searchtime, 'From What Time?' %><br>
								    	<%= s.select :searchtime, options_for_select(@searchtimes), {:prompt => ''}, {:style => 'width: 70%'}%>
								    </div> <br> 
								    
								    <div class="field">
									    <%= s.label :place, 'Pick a Location' %><br>
									    <%= s.select :place, options_for_select(@places), {:prompt => ''}, {:style => 'width: 70%'} %>
								    </div><br>
								    
								     <div class="field">
								    	<%= s.label :performer, 'Choose Perfomrer' %><br>
								    	<%= s.select :performer, options_for_select(@performers),{:prompt => ''}, {:style => 'width: 70%;'} %>
								    </div> <br>
								    
								    <div class="field">
									    <%= s.label :date, 'Choose a Date' %><br>
									    <%= s.text_field :date,:style => 'width: 70%;', :readonly => true, placeholder: "dd/mm/yy"%>
								    </div><br> <br>
								    					    	
								    	<div class="actions"><%= s.submit "Search", class: "btn btn-xl"%></div>
								    	
								    <%end%>	
								 </div>  					
							 </div>
			            </div>
			      </div>    	
		</section>

	
    	
    <!-- Contact Section -->
    <section id="contact">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-lg-12 text-center">
                    <h2 class="section-heading">Contact Us</h2>
                    <h3 class="section-subheading text-muted">Céad Míle Fáilte.</h3>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="row">
                 <%= form_for @contact, url: welcome_index_path, :html => {:id => 'foo'}, remote: true do |f| %>
                  <br/><br/>
                    <div class="col-md-6">
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <%= f.text_field  :name, :id => "name_input", required: true, class: "form-control", placeholder: "Full Name..." %></br>
                        </div>
                        
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <%= f.text_field :email, :id => "email_input", required: true, class: "form-control", placeholder: "Your Email Address..."%></br>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="col-md-6">
                        <div class="form-group">
                              <%= f.text_area :message, :id => "message_input", rows: 8, cols: 40, required: true, class: "form-control",
                                                placeholder: "Place Your Message Here..."%></br>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                      <div class= "hidden">
                        <%= f.label :nickname %>
                        <%= f.text_field :nickname, :hint => 'Leave this field blank!' %>
                      </div>
                      
                      <div class="col-md-12">
                          <div class="col-lg-12 text-center">
                                  <%= f.submit 'Send Message', :id => "form_button", class: 'btn btn-primary', data: { disable_with: "Submitting..."} %>
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-md-12" id="flash-message">
                                <%= render 'flash' %>
                            </div>
                      </div>
                      
                      <% end %>
              </div>
      </div>
            

 
